Interface CheckersGameListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
CheckersGUI, CheckersTrainer
public interface CheckersGameListener

An interface that has methods the CheckersGameManager will call to notify a listener of CheckersGameListener.CheckersGameEvents.

Version:
1.00 - 3 August 2008
Author:
Amos Yuen
